{"word":"G2020 - ἐπιφώσκω - epiphṓskō - ep-ee-foce'-ko - Begin to dawn","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιφώσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epiphṓskō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-foce'-ko</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Begin to dawn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விடி"},{"paragraph":"to grow light, to dawn"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A form of <a href=\"#/G2017 - ἐπιφαύω - epiphaúō - ep-ee-fow'-o/2017\">G2017</a>; to begin to <i>grow light:</i> - begin to dawn, X draw on.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2017/2017\">G2017</a>, <a href=\"#/G2020/2020\">G2020</a>, <a href=\"#/G5457/5457\">G5457</a>, <a href=\"#/G5458/5458\">G5458</a>, <a href=\"#/G5459/5459\">G5459</a>, <a href=\"#/G5460/5460\">G5460</a>, <a href=\"#/G5461/5461\">G5461</a>, <a href=\"#/G5462/5462\">G5462</a>"}]}